{"tid":2290762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教署: 在囚人士如果不住在區議員所屬區域 區議員不得以公務名義探訪","createTime":"2020-11-18T08:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T10:22:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b108d72c2b12d47d82ef97b404776331c99d77d6","tid":2290762,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"【懲教署繼續打壓公務探訪】#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n一直以來有為不同的在囚手足協助，一位手足未來的日子需要上庭，但家人對於法庭程序不算熟悉，所以我一直都有跟進和協助，也會就事件與他的代表律師溝通。<br />\n<br />\n本來打算在今天早上公務探訪，但一直未有收到回覆，直至今天回到辦公室才收到懲教署的回信，表示「上述在囚人士並非居於油尖旺區，公務探訪與香港法例第547章《區議會條例》第61(a) 條所列明的區議會職能無關」。似乎區議會條例已經變成尚方寶劍，民政專員覺得你要討論的東西不合乎他的心意和不合乎政府的立場，就借用這把尚方寶劍離場；同樣地懲教又動用這把尚方寶劍群魔亂舞。<br />\n<br />\n你說疫情而暫停公務探訪，勉強還說得過去。但你居然因為在囚人士並非居住在油尖旺區，而阻礙民選區議員支援在囚人士，向他們解釋他們應有的權利，以及協助處理法庭程序，這不是赤裸裸的政治打壓嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我經已去信要求懲教署回覆，我會為大家繼續跟進！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1887372994906575/posts/2649663002010900/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1887372994906575%2Fposts%2F2649663002010900%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1RYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=5a7442e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1887372994906575/posts/2649663002010900/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3f6fbc7ab28bb53076f697294bb6e7a4af6a4e73","tid":2290762,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55567fb7083b27a126261d6104fe47d30dba1b0b","tid":2290762,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817dbc823470f2df3bacc12a63a337a10faa0230","tid":2290762,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de2b3fd511dc952f24c716148526fc29f29d7fc","tid":2290762,"uid":112747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"但大灣區選民不住在區議員/立法會所屬區域 可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d562112f7cc0eca00639b2e50e596632292dfab7","tid":2290762,"uid":353501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff536e32a47ff3b504590a62cfd74bbe3d17239b","tid":2290762,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de2b3fd511dc952f24c716148526fc29f29d7fc","tid":2290762,"uid":112747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"但大灣區選民不住在區議員/立法會所屬區域 可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781625d14557dbad2c31d9a7d26c95db700e2303","tid":2290762,"uid":85629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"所以嗰啲成日話自己響政府裏面純粹打份工，個心好黃既黃墓員，如果你作為一個黃EO，老細要你打份咁嘅信，你都可以過到自己個關打到出嚟嘅，你真係唔好講個人黃<br />\n<br />\n底褲黃咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d846bf3ea580d0701fce9a76672dc7f20a1ec24a","tid":2290762,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"懲教狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9595b3641d5ffda145dc496d645d30b2fdc5df4","tid":2290762,"uid":203497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781625d14557dbad2c31d9a7d26c95db700e2303","tid":2290762,"uid":85629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"所以嗰啲成日話自己